{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"2s9lan55w6b9kb0909valdw","title":"Locations","desc":"","updated":1666316821031,"created":1666316821031,"custom":{},"fname":"world.locations","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"pmdwiki"},"contentHash":"edf513af104e6cd3409314516f49deee","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"world.locations","id":"2s9lan55w6b9kb0909valdw","vaultName":"pmdwiki"},"value":"world.locations.shelias-camp","alias":"Shelia's Camp","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":1,"offset":409},"end":{"line":8,"column":47,"offset":455},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"world.locations.shelias-camp"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"world.locations","id":"2s9lan55w6b9kb0909valdw","vaultName":"pmdwiki"},"value":"world.locations.Asterim","alias":"Asterim","position":{"start":{"line":14,"column":1,"offset":714},"end":{"line":14,"column":36,"offset":749},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"world.locations.Asterim"}},{"from":{"fname":"world","id":"meudvewf5oo11wq8mhf0kym","vaultName":"pmdwiki"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":13,"column":144,"offset":939},"end":{"line":13,"column":187,"offset":982},"indent":[]},"value":"world.locations"},{"from":{"fname":"root","id":"zh6cgxgxdu3u8nosydll2ik","vaultName":"pmdwiki"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":16,"column":4,"offset":756},"end":{"line":16,"column":23,"offset":775},"indent":[]},"value":"world.locations"}],"anchors":{"settlements":{"type":"header","text":"Settlements","value":"settlements","line":10,"column":0,"depth":2},"notable-settlements":{"type":"header","text":"Notable Settlements","value":"notable-settlements","line":13,"column":0,"depth":3},"towns":{"type":"header","text":"Towns","value":"towns","line":16,"column":0,"depth":2},"notable-towns":{"type":"header","text":"Notable Towns","value":"notable-towns","line":19,"column":0,"depth":3}},"children":["1qv5bt0exb5d0j8bll46s25","nniyqfu2hjqy42jv8kw0abx"],"parent":"meudvewf5oo11wq8mhf0kym","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"locations\">Locations<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#locations\"></a></h1>\n<p>The settlements and towns of the island consist entirely of various pokemon. Coming together, either be that by necessity, force, or willingness. They are all a part of the ecosystem at large.</p>\n<h2 id=\"settlements\">Settlements<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#settlements\"></a></h2>\n<p>Settlements are dotted everywhere throughout the island, and generally have a population size of >5-15 people. Small and quaint, are mostly comprised of friends or families.</p>\n<h3 id=\"notable-settlements\">Notable Settlements<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#notable-settlements\"></a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/notes/nniyqfu2hjqy42jv8kw0abx\">Shelia's Camp</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"towns\">Towns<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#towns\"></a></h2>\n<p>Towns can be considered gathering hubs for large swaths of pokémon. They can easily reach the hundreds and have some form of trade present. They usually contain general shops, banks, or other things needed for passing travelers.</p>\n<h3 id=\"notable-towns\">Notable Towns<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#notable-towns\"></a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"/notes/1qv5bt0exb5d0j8bll46s25\">Asterim</a> (Ruins)</p>\n<hr>\n<strong>Children</strong>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/1qv5bt0exb5d0j8bll46s25\">Asterim</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/nniyqfu2hjqy42jv8kw0abx\">Shelia's Camp</a></li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/meudvewf5oo11wq8mhf0kym\">Undr Öld - The Wondrous World</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/\">The Wondrous World</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"zh6cgxgxdu3u8nosydll2ik","title":"The Wondrous World","desc":"","updated":1666599474864,"created":1666316457940,"custom":{"nav_order":0,"permalink":"/"},"fname":"root","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"pmdwiki"},"contentHash":"7d4ec587097283e431c6b0171d591530","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"zh6cgxgxdu3u8nosydll2ik","vaultName":"pmdwiki"},"value":"world","alias":"World","position":{"start":{"line":15,"column":1,"offset":698},"end":{"line":15,"column":16,"offset":713},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"world"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"zh6cgxgxdu3u8nosydll2ik","vaultName":"pmdwiki"},"value":"world.locations","position":{"start":{"line":16,"column":4,"offset":756},"end":{"line":16,"column":23,"offset":775},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"world.locations"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"zh6cgxgxdu3u8nosydll2ik","vaultName":"pmdwiki"},"value":"people","alias":"People","position":{"start":{"line":18,"column":1,"offset":836},"end":{"line":18,"column":18,"offset":853},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"people"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"zh6cgxgxdu3u8nosydll2ik","vaultName":"pmdwiki"},"value":"great-catastrophes","alias":"The Great Catastrophes","position":{"start":{"line":20,"column":1,"offset":914},"end":{"line":20,"column":46,"offset":959},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"great-catastrophes"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"root","id":"zh6cgxgxdu3u8nosydll2ik","vaultName":"pmdwiki"},"value":"world-fracture","alias":"The World Fracture","position":{"start":{"line":23,"column":1,"offset":1001},"end":{"line":23,"column":38,"offset":1038},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"world-fracture"}}],"anchors":{"outline":{"type":"header","text":"Outline","value":"outline","line":20,"column":0,"depth":1}},"children":["wf0akia7teumrr2uz9ahcai","mbgjs3d1copv01e81nxy0nf","s75uxhz7wr8b0mzu8my18j1","7fcovynnlt7sbqti1o0ne8m","68b3yfsvjy3nurxncttcj2g","meudvewf5oo11wq8mhf0kym"],"parent":null,"data":{},"body":"![pmdlogo.png](assets/pmdlogo.png){max-width: 195px, float: left, margin: 20px}\n\nThe world of Undr Öld - in english, The Wondrous World! This is an island untouched by humanity, shrouded in mystery, with adventures far larger than it alone! The inhabitants are comprised entirely of Pokémon! \n\nThis wiki is a part of my Pokerole campaign. If you're a player of said campaign, 1. how did you find this and 2. Please click off this has major spoilers!\n\nBelow you can see the Outline of various pages and points of interest within the world!\n\nThis is a *private* campaign and as a result there will be no publicly available VoDs for this campaign.\n\nThe PMD logo was made by kiwi_p0yo\n<br/>\n\n# Outline\n[[World|world]] - Brief overview of the World at large\n - [[world.locations]] - An explanation of the settlements that inhabit the world\n\n[[People|people]] - The various and notable Pokémon that can be encountered!\n\n[[The Great Catastrophes|great-catastrophes]] - Major events that disrupt the island\n\n\n[[The World Fracture|world-fracture]] - The source of the great catastrophes and happenings in the world."},"collectionChildren":null,"customHeadContent":null,"config":{"version":5,"dev":{"enablePreviewV2":true,"enableSelfContainedVaults":true},"commands":{"lookup":{"note":{"selectionMode":"extract","confirmVaultOnCreate":true,"vaultSelectionModeOnCreate":"smart","leaveTrace":false,"bubbleUpCreateNew":true,"fuzzThreshold":0.2}},"randomNote":{},"insertNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"none","enableMultiSelect":false},"insertNoteIndex":{"enableMarker":false},"copyNoteLink":{"aliasMode":"title"},"templateHierarchy":"template"},"workspace":{"vaults":[{"fsPath":".","selfContained":true,"name":"pmdwiki"}],"journal":{"dailyDomain":"daily","name":"journal","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd","addBehavior":"childOfDomain"},"scratch":{"name":"scratch","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd.HHmmss","addBehavior":"asOwnDomain"},"task":{"name":"task","dateFormat":"y.MM.dd","addBehavior":"asOwnDomain","statusSymbols":{"":" ","wip":"w","done":"x"